160|2011-10-06|As I already mentioned, you have been President of the ECB for 8 years, the last 4 years of which have proved very demanding.|8|0.24242424242424243|OTHER_IRRELEVANT|0.3216957449913025
160|2011-10-06|It is no overstatement when I say, that, Jean-Claude has fought passionately and with tireless and unconditional conviction to overcome the European debt crisis.|9|0.2727272727272727|FISCAL_AND_STRUCTURAL|0.5677812099456787
